snippet.title: Project Agora (Official Teaser Trailer)
snippet.description: Project AG is a third Person fighting game in the style of a 1v1/2v2 . Bringing back the paragon heroes we all loved and held , The set early access release will be in 2021 . Some Heroes will be Reworked and ALL heroes will be re- balanced to fight the 1v1 arena style
